{"tid":1578771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"臨近國慶難翻牆<環時>老總都抱怨","createTime":"2019-09-18T09:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T12:20:15.000Z","uid":97435,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"267318aac82aeb52672f840d31b87a8aaa5f32a0","tid":1578771,"uid":97435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"臨近十一國慶，北京加強保安，網絡防火牆城似乎也「加固」，令官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進今日在微博發文，抱怨「國慶節快到了，上外網極其艱難，連《環球時報》的工作都受了影響」。胡認為當局此舉「有些過了」，又強調中國人大多數「愛國愛黨，有強大的政治分辨能力，立場堅定」，而且「這個國家並不脆弱」，建議當局「相信群眾」，並「在社會和外網之間多留出一些縫隙」，這既對中國輿論場的強大與成熟有利，亦對科研、對外溝通及國家利益有益。<br />\n目前這篇抱怨文已經刪除，有網民則已截圖轉發，有人在截圖下留言稱，「是他VPN有問題吧，我這可順了」，但亦有人指「這周一開始，我的VPN不能用了」、「VPN直接提示，關門謝客一月」，還有人質疑，「他們報社都有專門的通道，這是奉命呼籲而已」。另有人表示，「建立大國自信，也要從這些細節入手」。<br />\n<br />\nSource:聖誕快樂報<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/share/189304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fshare%2F189304&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=4cb333d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/share/189304</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ac50e9c923fac40a53f4987858dda7a91b2e74","tid":1578771,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:14:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29614e82dfe49aff851025f0b4012da3ebae7e26","tid